# Cursor Rules

Use `AGENTS.md` as the canonical instruction file for this repository.

- Read `AGENTS.md` first for runtime, architecture, and repo conventions.
- For UI or frontend work, read `.impeccable.md` and `documentation/STYLEGUIDE.md`.
- For copy, docs, prompts, and user-facing text, read `documentation/skill.md`.
- Preserve the existing CRM design language. Do not introduce generic AI SaaS visuals or a second competing design system.
